cast.name: 弗兰丹尼可·达尔·汉森 Frederikke Dahl Hansen
艾历克斯·休·安德森 Alex Høgh Andersen

introduction: Following the ups-and-downs of Sylvia and Mikkel as time passes, One of Us is Trembling traces the story of a young couple and dissects the troubled psyches of the characters played by Frederikke Dahl Hansen and Alex Høgh Andersen (Vikings). As raw as it is delicate, the series captures the excitement of a first encounter, the passion and pain that shapes the myth of a love story, and the ongoing struggle with oneself.
